Ruff paws? Heal them. Scratchy paws are more than uncomfortable, they can become more prone to injury from splitting and cracking. #PawSoother is amazing for keeping paws healthy! It’s organic, all-natural, pet-safe and it works fast to heal dry & rough paw pads.
.
